  "url": "https://www.lankadeepa.lk/latest_news/\u0da2\u0dd3\u0dc0\u0db1-\u0db6\u0dbb-\u0d85\u0da9\u0dd4-\u0d9a\u0dbb\u0db1\u0dca\u0db1-\u0dbb\u0db1\u0dd2\u0dbd\u0dca\u0d9c\u0dd9\u0db1\u0dca-\u0dc3\u0dc4\u0db1/1-616530",
  "time_ut": 1657978713,
  "original_lang": "si",
  "original_title": "\u0da2\u0dd3\u0dc0\u0db1 \u0db6\u0dbb \u0d85\u0da9\u0dd4 \u0d9a\u0dbb\u0db1\u0dca\u0db1 \u0dbb\u0db1\u0dd2\u0dbd\u0dca\u0d9c\u0dd9\u0db1\u0dca \u0dc3\u0dc4\u0db1",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Relief from Ranil to reduce the burden of life",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Acting President Ranil Wickramasinghe has decided to start a relief program to reduce the burden of the people who are under severe economic pressure.",
        "In a discussion with Ministers and Members of Parliament, the Acting President has said that since the prices of fuel, gas and essential food items have increased rapidly, he has decided to start an urgent relief program to reduce the living burden of the people.",
        "In addition to this quick relief program, the President has also decided to use additional funds to reduce the burden of living and provide relief in the relief budget presented next August.",
        "In that discussion, the Acting President has advised to speed up the actions of the food security program and strengthen the process.",
        "The attention of the Acting President has also been focused on setting up a system to provide fuel and fertilizer to the people in a regular and prompt manner.",
        "Also, it has been noticed in this discussion that they should prepare the necessary environment to run their business without hindrance."
      ],
